    "However, there emerges an ethical issue when applying these systems in those areas where the users may not willingly offer their consent.",
    "Implementing anonymization techniques and assuring the transparency of data processing and utilization by the models also helps minimize privacy threats while maintaining a high level of safety.",
    "Last but not least, security and privacy must always be in parity, and well-defined dispersion, retention, and usage of network data must be in place.",
